E_D("replace into `xcaity_ecms_news_data_1` values('4','2','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p>For the removal of people may moving is short, may also be a long-distance move, for example from Shijiazhuang moved to Beijing even if is long-distance move, today Xiaobian want to share with you is long-distance move matters we need to pay attention to what, how to do a good job in the long-distance moving things.<br />\r\n1. Start to organize things that don\\\\''t often use.. For example: the book, out of season clothes, is often used for food or ornaments.<br />\r\n2, a room packing list only. Because it will forget what the box, so, do not mix the items of the room in a better packing.<br />\r\n3, heavy box, big zoom box. Heavy objects such as books, porcelain, antiques, if a big box of handling will be very hard, so the packaging into the small box.<br />\r\n4, will be the name of the goods outside the carton. After the packing is complete, please be sure that the room number of the item name and new house is marked out in the box..<br />\r\n5, the packing should not have the gap. If there is a gap in the box, the items will easily move, and lead to damage. If you do not carefully have the gap, then the newspaper as a buffer equipment in the fixed box items.<br />\r\n6, pay attention not too full. The case of excessive easy to deformation, may lead to damage in the box of goods, in addition, in the box may be due to uneven and collapse, which is very dangerous.</p>');");
E_D("replace into `xcaity_ecms_news_data_1` values('5','2','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p>Do not know you have not found a situation, we at the time of consumption, are often the first to consider is the cost, first look at the brand of the product price, with a brand of things, must be considered low price of the. Even now moving expenses is the same reason, many citizens in Changchun in the choice of Changchun moving company move, will be the first to consider the issue of cost price, if the price is low, it is estimated that a lot of people will be preferred. Even if the same home, the same brand of the moving company, they will certainly choose the low cost. Is the price of the price considered right when choosing the moving company?<br />\r\nThe first thing is to find the owners move before the move, now most moving companies are not regular personal, moving companies, but their service with the name of the company in the one hundred and eight thousand gap is so smooth, the owners want to move is not to find regular moving company, so how to find a good point the moving company moving company Changchun? Xiaobian recommend, not only in the network can be found on many moving companies can be compared, and you can ask your friends to have a look, there is no one responsible for the better the moving company, a number of channels to find, then carries on the contrast analysis, find the one that is best for you the moving company.<br />\r\nMove not plan to save money, and some irregular moving company price is very low, but always do some unsatisfactory things, that count down, money not only did not spend less, moreover also has a stomach gas, why?? small series suggest that consumers, in order to save money, early find the regular moving company, they are not only good service, and fees are not high to move before the matters needing attention.<br />\r\nHow to save the cost of moving, many customers mistakenly believe that to save the moving costs must find thos