E_D("replace into `xcaity_ecms_news_data_1` values('6','2','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p>In addition to wine culture in China, should belong to the gift is the most easy to draw people. For the movers, entertain relatives and friends is very common, then guests cannot empty handed and need to meaning. So a friend move we actually send what good?, this is a question worthy of the probe, to send good can be closer to the distance, send bad will produce estrangement.<br />\r\nHas received a lot of friends dinner move when a lot of people will send what gift to worry, if the relatives and friends move is not a large dinner guests, or close relationship, under normal circumstances we are to send money. This time my friends told us to actually not for money, but you have a warm place, look lively, increase indoor popularity, and let these friends recognize the door can often come around, for after the two sides have difficulties can help each other to provide a basis. This time we want to send a gift, in fact, flowers is a very good choice. Different flowers in different ways, so we have to send more means booming, auspicious flowers.<br />\r\nFlowers can add vigor and vitality to the new house, so we choose flowers is a good idea. If the owner of the house is the young couple or just get married soon we can send lily, indicating that the life of conjugal bliss, then a lot of newly married couples are very like. People to middle-aged\\\\''s biggest problem is the career, so if it is middle-aged people we can send hollyhock, gladiolus, meaning the steadily rising, but if the middle-aged man, in business has been in a steady state the, we can iris, meaning the happy life, because a person if in business has been in a stable state after, in his heart the hope they can further stabilize is own life, hope have a can be anchored to the harbor.<br />\r\nA measure often cannot be measured in dollars of friendship between friends, so do not reflect the value of small flowers. Flowers is a learned some things, so to master some necessary skills, in order to narrow the distance between people.</p>');");
E_D("replace into `xcaity_ecms_news_data_1` values('7','2','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p>For some recent need to move the friends before moving to prepare the matter is very necessary and good understanding of these matters will be carried out smoothly finish move, happy to move to the new premises. Today, a small series to talk about moving house time to move the schedule matters:<br />\r\nFirst of all, to confirm the time to move. Only after the moving time to confirm the work after the good arrangement. Generally speaking, moving time by the influence of many factors, for example, relocation destination whether can arrange live and move out to the arrangement of whether ready to move out, moving the date whether and work time or an important event in the conflict. , how much time is needed to advance the sorting and so on. These are all to be noted..<br />\r\nSecond, booking Changchun moving company. OK after moving the next step is to find a more appropriate moving company. With the moving company to determine the time to move, goods, routes, fees, etc., in the two sides agreed to confirm the time to move again after the two parties. Appointment should ask attention to each other is individual moving company or regular moving company, whether to issue formal invoice to move, whether can move of signing the contract etc., move you must move the contract agreement signed. This is the most important book rights. Above is the move in the process of the need to pay attention to the points, we can read, at the same time, with the help of the Beijing more regular moving company - Tai Hing moving company relocation. Beijing has many large and small moving company, moving company in Changchun in the relocation process attaches great importance to the items up and management, usually an individual move, home have many small items, the debris and daily necessities is need to pack, and is also the most difficult to clean up, most likely to be lost.<br />\r\nIn order to be