E_D("replace into `xcaity_ecms_news_data_1` values('10','1','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p>WELCOME TO FASTRAK MOVER , INC. .</p>\r\n<p>FASTRAK MOVER (CAL P.U.C. T-191084) has served over hundreds families and companies for their moves in many different local areas - San Francisco, Palo Alto. Sacramento, Santa Clara, Mountain View, Cupertino, San Ramon, Walnut Creek and Milpitas etc; As well as long distance areas - Los Angeles, Orange County, Reno, Las Vegas and Oregon.</p>\r\n<p>&quot;One Call, Set, Go!&quot;</p>\r\n<p>We\\\\''ve simplified moving. Here are five of the things we have learned.</p>\r\n<p>1. How soon will you need to move? From our experience, you know you will need to move within a week, most probably 2 days. We will reserve you a dedicated moving team once we finish our call.</p>\r\n<p>2. How far will you need to go? Local moving takes about 3 to 4 hours.</p>\r\n<p>Long distance moving gives you options of same day delivery or over night delivery to the door. You can choose to take a rest in the evening and get it going the other day morning.</p>\r\n<p>3. How much stuff do you have? Multiple-room apartments or one single room studio of furniture? Small offices or whole floor of commerical equipments? We are specialized in different difficult stuff, e.g.&nbsp; upright or grand&nbsp; pianos, refrigerators, sofas, closets or shelves.</p>\r\n<p>4. How many strong movers do you need? We provide minimum two efficient and friendly movers depends on your move. You live on the fifth floor and you have a refrigerator. The building has no elevator but you have us. We will send you an extra mover with an affordable and reasonable rate.</p>\r\n<p>5. Do you have any special valuable properties, says, antiques or artwork? We always provide full insurance and extra care. So don\\\\''t be scared.</p>\r\n<p>Call today and receive a Free Quote at (510) 612-5538.</p>\r\n<p>One Call, Set, Go!</p>\r\n<p>WE PROMISE SATISFACTION</p>\r\n<p>Lucky Star Moving is a family owned and locally operated moving company serving San Francisco Bay Area. We are licensed (CAL P.U.C. T-191084) with State of California Public Utilities Commission and abide by the rules and regulations of CPUC. We are fully insured. The cargo insurance provides for recovery for lost or damaged items up to<br />\r\n\$1,000,000.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>');");
